Package sealey.javafxinventorysystem.models

Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
sealey.javafxinventorysystem.models.Inventory
public class Inventory extends Object
The Inventory class contains a list of all products and parts in the inventory, methods to retrieve and set the lists; and methods to update, add, lookup, and delete individual parts and products.
Author:
Max Sealey

    • lookupPart

      public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<Part> lookupPart(String partName)
      lookupPart() ia an overloaded method that searches through the list of Parts and returns a list of all objects containing the search term. Not case-sensitive
      Parameters:
      partName - search term to look for in each Part's name
      Returns:
      temp List of parts where the search term is contained in the part's name
